b-inspired\/","url_meta":{"origin":20108,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Umar: If anyone in Ummah is divinely-inspired, it is Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBefore you were nations with divinely inspired people. If such a person were in my nation, it would surely be Umar.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3689 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13893,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/02\/no-salat-bathroom\/","url_meta":{"origin":20108,"position":5},"title":"Umar on Salat: No praying if you need to relieve yourself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 2, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Aslam reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cLet not one of you pray while holding his bowels.\u201d Source: al-Muwat\u0323t\u0323a' 381 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0637\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064f\u0635\u064e\u0644\u0650\u0651\u064a\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u062